cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a fully integrated autonomous multi-robot aerial system for search and rescue robotics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the system uses blob detection, inverse 3D-projection, and visual-servoing for object detection and tracking. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the system uses Kalman filtering for object tracking. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the system uses accurate global state estimation and reactive collision avoidance. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is relevant as the system uses sweep planning for multi-agent exploration.
